  <brief_title>Oral Contraceptives as Infertility Treatments for Premature Ovarian Failure</brief_title>
  <official_title>Drospirenone and Ethinyl Estradiol Combinations (Yasmin) as Infertility Treatments for Premature Ovarian Failure: a Perspective Follow-up Study.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
